description: Try our easy to follow Baby's Chicken And Asparagus Purée recipe. Absolutely delicious with the best ingredients from Woolworths.

name: Baby's Chicken And Asparagus Purée Recipe | Woolworths

recipeInstructions.text: Prepare noodles according to packet directions.
Heat 1 teaspoon of oil in a wok over medium-high heat. Stir-fry asparagus and 2 tablespoons water. Cover with lid or foil. Cook for 3 minutes or until tender and bright green. Set aside.

Heat wok until dry. Add remaining oil in wok. Stir-fry chicken in 3 batches for 2 minutes or until cooked. Combine chicken, noodles, vegetables and 1/2 cup water in a blender. Purée to desired consistency for baby’s developmental age. (Add a little more water if your baby prefers it smoother). Serves 10 baby portions
